import React from 'react'
import Helmet from '../components/Helmet/Helmet'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap'

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Helmet title = {'Home'}>
      <section className="heroSection">
        <Container>
          <Row>
            <Col lg = '6' md = '5'></Col>
          </Row>
        </Container>
      </section>
    </Helmet>
  )
}

export default Home
